beer.beer_description: This mid-strength lager is crafted using ultra-high gravity brewing to increase body and intensity of flavour. Late hopped with Amarillo, the signature citrus flavour thread throughout the Cricketers Arms range. The Journeyman was inspired by the Cricketers Arms founders who have enjoyed life’s journey and infused that into this beer. Excellent with chilli prawns and calamari.
